file.name: evemarketer.com-1.0.1-swagger.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  contact:
    x-twitter: EVEMarketer
  description: EVEMarketer Marketstat API is almost compatible with EVE-Central's
    Marketstat API.
  title: EVEMarketer Marketstat
  version: 1.0.1
  x-apisguru-categories:
    - entertainment
  x-logo:
    url: https://twitter.com/EVEMarketer/profile_image?size=original
  x-origin:
    - format: swagger
      url: https://api.evemarketer.com/ec/swagger.yaml
      version: "2.0"
  x-providerName: evemarketer.com
tags:
  - description: marketstat
    name: marketstat
paths:
  /marketstat:
    get:
      parameters:
        - description: >
            TypeID. Multiple TypeIDs can be specified in the following format
            (up to 200 TypeIDs per request):

            typeid=34&typeid=35 or typeid=34,35
          in: query
          name: typeid
          required: true
          schema:
            type: array
            items:
              format: int32
              type: integer
        - description: Limit the statistics to a single region.
          in: query
          name: regionlimit
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
        - description: Limit the statistics to a single solar system.
          in: query
          name: usesystem
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successful Request
          headers:
            X-Ratelimit-Limit:
              description: The number of allowed requests in the current period
              schema:
                type: integer
            X-Ratelimit-Remaining:
              description: The number of remaining requests in the current period
              schema:
                type: integer
            X-Ratelimit-Reset:
              description: The time at which the current rate limit window resets in UTC
                epoch seconds.
              schema:
                type: integer
          content:
            application/xml:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/ExecAPI"
        "400":
          description: Invalid Parameters
        "429":
          description: Rate limit exceeded
      summary: XML Marketstat
      tags:
        - marketstat
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          multipart/form-data:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                typeid:
                  description: >
                    TypeID. Multiple TypeIDs can be specified in the following
                    format (up to 200 TypeIDs per request):

                    typeid=34&typeid=35 or typeid=34,35
                  type: array
                  items:
                    format: int32
                    type: integer
                regionlimit:
                  description: Limit the statistics to a single region.
                  type: integer
                  format: int32
                usesystem:
                  description: Limit the statistics to a single solar system.
                  type: integer
                  format: int32
              required:
                - typeid
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successful Request
          headers:
            X-Ratelimit-Limit:
              description: The number of allowed requests in the current period
              schema:
                type: integer
            X-Ratelimit-Remaining:
              description: The number of remaining requests in the current period
              schema:
                type: integer
            X-Ratelimit-Reset:
              description: The time at which the current rate limit window resets in UTC
                epoch seconds.
              schema:
                type: integer
          content:
            application/xml:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/ExecAPI"
        "400":
          description: Invalid Parameters
        "429":
          description: Rate limit exceeded
      summary: XML Marketstat
      tags:
        - marketstat
  /marketstat/json:
    get:
      requestBody:
        content:
          multipart/form-data:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                typeid:
                  description: >
                    TypeID. Multiple TypeIDs can be specified in the following
                    format (up to 200 TypeIDs per request):

                    typeid=34&typeid=35 or typeid=34,35
                  type: array
                  items:
                    format: int32
                    type: integer
                regionlimit:
                  description: Limit the statistics to a single region.
                  type: integer
                  format: int32
                usesystem:
                  description: Limit the statistics to a single region.
                  type: integer
                  format: int32
              required:
                - typeid
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successful Request
          headers:
            X-Ratelimit-Limit:
              description: The number of allowed requests in the current period
              schema:
                type: integer
            X-Ratelimit-Remaining:
              description: The number of remaining requests in the current period
              schema:
                type: integer
            X-Ratelimit-Reset:
              description: The time at which the current rate limit window resets in UTC
                epoch seconds.
              schema:
                type: integer
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                items:
                  $ref: "#/components/schemas/Type"
                type: array
        "400":
          description: Invalid Parameters
        "429":
          description: Rate limit exceeded
      summary: JSON Marketstat
      tags:
        - marketstat
    post:
      parameters:
        - description: >
            TypeID. Multiple TypeIDs can be specified in the following format
            (up to 200 TypeIDs per request):

            typeid=34&typeid=35 or typeid=34,35
          in: query
          name: typeid
          required: true
          schema:
            type: array
            items:
              format: int32
              type: integer
        - description: Limit the statistics to a single region.
          in: query
          name: regionlimit
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
        - description: Limit the statistics to a single region.
          in: query
          name: usesystem
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successful Request
          headers:
            X-Ratelimit-Limit:
              description: The number of allowed requests in the current period
              schema:
                type: integer
            X-Ratelimit-Remaining:
              description: The number of remaining requests in the current period
              schema:
                type: integer
            X-Ratelimit-Reset:
              description: The time at which the current rate limit window resets in UTC
                epoch seconds.
              schema:
                type: integer
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                items:
                  $ref: "#/components/schemas/Type"
                type: array
        "400":
          description: Invalid Parameters
        "429":
          description: Rate limit exceeded
      summary: JSON Marketstat
      tags:
        - marketstat
servers:
  - url: https://api.evemarketer.com/ec
components:
  schemas:
    ExecAPI:
      properties:
        marketstat:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/MarketStatXML"
        method:
          example: marketstat_xml
          type: string
          xml:
            attribute: true
        version:
          example: "2.0"
          type: string
          xml:
            attribute: true
      type: object
    ForQuery:
      properties:
        bid:
          description: is buy?
          type: boolean
        hours:
          description: always 0
          format: int32
          type: integer
        minq:
          description: always 0
          format: int32
          type: integer
        regions:
          description: Region IDs
          items:
            example: 10000002
            format: int32
            type: integer
          type: array
        systems:
          description: System IDs
          items:
            format: int32
            type: integer
          type: array
        types:
          description: Type IDs
          items:
            example: 44992
            format: int32
            type: integer
          type: array
      type: object
    MarketStatXML:
      items:
        properties:
          buy:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/TypeStatXML"
          sell:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/TypeStatXML"
        type: object
      type: array
    Type:
      properties:
        buy:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/TypeStat"
        sell:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/TypeStat"
      type: object
    TypeStat:
      properties:
        avg:
          description: Average Price
          example: 3352708.11
          format: double
          type: number
        fivePercent:
          example: 2949353.31
          format: double
          type: number
        forQuery:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/ForQuery"
        generated:
          description: Generated at (UNIX Timestamp msec)
          example: 1499280224508
          format: int64
          type: integer
        highToLow:
          type: boolean
        max:
          example: 10000000
          format: double
          type: number
        median:
          description: Median Price
          example: 3094978.97
          format: double
          type: number
        min:
          example: 2601400.03
          format: double
          type: number
        stdDev:
          description: Standard Deviation
          example: 877391.25
          format: double
          type: number
        variance:
          example: 769815422537.24
          format: double
          type: number
        volume:
          description: Order Volume
          example: 963208
          format: int64
          type: integer
        wavg:
          description: Weighted Average Price
          example: 3204519.59
          format: double
          type: number
      type: object
    TypeStatXML:
      properties:
        avg:
          description: Weighted Average Price
          example: 3204519.59
          format: double
          type: number
        max:
          description: Maximum Price
          example: 10000000
          format: double
          type: number
        median:
          description: Median Price
          example: 3094978.97
          format: double
          type: number
        min:
          description: Minimum Price
          example: 2601400.03
          format: double
          type: number
        percentile:
          description: 5% Price
          example: 2949353.31
          format: double
          type: number
        stddev:
          description: Standard Deviation
          example: 877391.25
          format: double
          type: number
        volume:
          description: Order Volume
          example: 963208
          format: int64
          type: integer
      type: object
